'''''Place of Weeping''''' (ikinamico nka '''Afrika - Land der Hoffnung''' )<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/1986/12/05/movies/the-screen-place-of-weeping.html</ref>, ni filime y'ikinamico yo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afrika yepfo]] yasohotse muri 1986 yayobowe na Darrell Roodt ikanakorwa na Anant Singh muri Place of Weeping Productions<ref>https://www.movieposters.com/products/place-of-weeping-mpw-33366</ref>.   Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo James Whyle, Gcina Mhlophe na Charles Comyn mu bakinnyi ba mbere mu gihe Norman Coombes, Michelle du Toit, Kerneels Coertzen na Patrick Shai bagize uruhare runini<ref>https://www.tvguide.com/movies/place-of-weeping/review/2000344626/</ref><ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/au/film335425.html</ref>.   Iyi filime isobanura mu buryo burambuye ku matsinda y’imico myinshi yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'epfo n’uburyo [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo yaguye kubera ibikorwa by’abanyafurika yepfo n’amakimbirane mu butegetsi bukandamiza [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo<ref>https://mubi.com/films/a-place-for-weeping</ref>. Iyi niyo shusho yambere yo kurwanya ivanguramoko yakozwe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo<ref>https://www.clevelandfilm.org/films/1987/place-of-weeping</ref>. Filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku ya 5 Ukuboza 1986. Filime yakiriwe neza nabayireba<ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b7588f5c5</ref>.  

